958
00:59:06,485 --> 00:59:09,087
Já jsem hlavní chirurg.

959
00:59:09,254 --> 00:59:11,456
Cože? Kde je doktor Lee?

960
00:59:17,062 --> 00:59:17,796
Doktore,

961
00:59:18,530 --> 00:59:19,698
